Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.20,0:00:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should ask me first
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.67,0:00:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before taking on a task.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.75,0:00:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.21,0:00:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we help?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:00:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.62,0:00:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This suspect is cunning and seasoned,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:01:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his modus operandi\Nis extremely meticulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.37,0:01:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only surveillance photo\Nthat managed to capture his image.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What crime did he commit?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.54,0:01:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There have been frequent\Nhomicides happening lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were no obvious motives\Nfor these murders,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and there were no specific connections\Namong the victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.45,0:01:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we've deduced that\Nthis is probably a serial homicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.54,0:01:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, based on the clues\Nwe have so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.83,0:01:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems that finding the killer\Nis not going to be that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.25,0:01:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.37,0:01:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an inhuman pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.91,0:01:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.21,0:01:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is imperative that\Nwe help with this case!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.41,0:01:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to catch him as soon as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to prevent someone else\Nfrom becoming a victim!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.91,0:01:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheng Xiaoshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.46,0:01:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who gave you the right to speak for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Xiao, don't listen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.17,0:01:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still up to Lu Guang\Nto decide whether or not we can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.58,0:01:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've looked at the general situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.54,0:01:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Lu Guang, that's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see it clearly?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lu Guang,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,did you look at the photos carefully?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.54,0:02:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.04,0:02:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is such a big case,\Nit's not a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I trust Lu Guang's judgment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lu Guang,\Nare you sure you saw it clearly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You rarely ever say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.83,0:03:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was the one who\Nwanted to take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, but after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,um, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and receive guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, my landlady...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, welcome in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Xu Shanshan, why are you here\Ninstead of studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here because I care about\Nthe reemployment of the jobless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you're here to observe\Nthe regular people's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.79,0:04:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no wonder,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.08,0:04:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after all, it's easy to grow out of touch\Nwith society after studying so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unlike certain people,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who has rely on others\Nto survive even after graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your words,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who's relying on whom to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.54,0:04:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The house is provided by Qiao,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the business is managed by Lu Guang,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,aren't you just a good-for-nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are partners!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't poison the well if you don't\Nunderstand the situation clearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only look at the surface of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have such low EQ!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have I always told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must be considerate and\Nattentive to our customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What customers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, if it wasn't Qiao who convinced me\Nto come and give it a try,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't even want to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shanshan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what do you need help with?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let me tell you about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To begin,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.04,0:04:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let us return to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our vigorous
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:05:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,university days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,aside from the three of us,\Nthere was another good friend
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hanging around our beautiful Miss Xu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dong Yi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.04,0:05:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you'll have to help me take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come and get it from you at\Nyour dormitory after I get back tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the entrance of\Nthe dormitory is locked,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:05:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to throw it down to you\Nfrom the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of you are basically like\Nan old married couple,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why not clarify your relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pfft,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,shouldn't boys take the initiative\Nin such matters?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dong Yi,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, this is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two fried eggs, slightly spicy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one sausage, no coriander.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, how much is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll transfer the money to you via WeChat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.62,0:05:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talking about money hurts relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk about\Nother conditions, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally reached Platinum!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My ranking is King,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's more than enough to carry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something growing in my brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I getting a headache\Nafter just a few rounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you laughing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.96,0:06:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you even have a conscience?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if there's something\Nbad growing in my brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.42,0:06:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This problem is happening\Nto younger people nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Dong Yi were actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the one with the low EQ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alas, it's been so many years,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yet the secret's still not out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is driving me crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Postgraduate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so shocked?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to further my studies,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which will give me a higher chance\Nof getting a better job in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.45,0:06:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful Miss Xu,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the next two years,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be by your side,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you'll have to\Ntake good care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.54,0:06:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.33,0:06:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who usually takes care of whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you gone,\NI can relax a lot more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh wow, so you've always hated\Nhaving to put up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But deep down in my heart I knew,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:07:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that she decided to stay behind\Nbecause of Dong Yi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That tutor is awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All he cares about\Nis his business outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.91,0:07:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We hardly get to see him at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop complaining about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have to rely on ourselves then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she waited for the sentence\Nthat never came.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like an arrow, time flew by,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the blink of an eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,two years of postgraduate studies\Npassed in a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've graduated again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, after bachelor's degree,\Nit's master's,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after master's, it's doctorate,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.83,0:07:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's continue studying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I'm done with studying,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to look for a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.33,0:07:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'll drink to that!\N--Xu Shanshan,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--All good things must come to an end.\N--take a photo with Dong Yi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here, why are you so shy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking,\Nyou're so old-fashioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I only have\Ntwo photos from that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the other one is a selfie\NI took for fun before dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheng Xiaoshi, you're so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you tell us about\Nthe specifics of the task first?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I'll pick a suitable photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you the rest of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the farewell dinner,\Nwe went to a karaoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:07:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It ended pretty late,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and somehow,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I drank a little too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.66,0:08:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.12,0:08:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's not what you think it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bye-bye!\N--See you guys next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope you all get rich in the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's keep in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, my fellow classmates!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, Dong Yi,\N--Hey, Xu Shanshan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--be careful.\N--Let's keep in touch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bye!\N--Let's go, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sure!\N--Keep in touch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go, no one is allowed to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.21,0:08:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're all already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should join me\Nfor another round!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The signal is pretty weak here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get a ride,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.16,0:08:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go over to that side and try.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them can leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.04,0:08:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except for you,\Nyou're not allowed to go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xu Shanshan,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, I blacked out,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hear a single word he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After sobering up, I realised I had\Ndone lots of embarrassing things,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and got myself in trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.58,0:08:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I regret it so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you care so much about what he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why didn't you just ask him\Nabout it afterward?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I care so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's why I couldn't bring myself to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so afraid that the answer\Nis not going to be what I think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pfft, how dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.08,0:09:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can help you with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You agree, just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey wait a minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,did you say help?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is clearly a deal,\Nwhy should we do it for free?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She should at least give us\Na little something in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.16,0:09:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheng Xiaoshi! You traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just trying to pay off your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if you're willing to give\Na discount, that's fine as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, it seems his brain\Ncan't function properly
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without a beating a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Qiao,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how are they able to\Nget information of the past from photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.66,0:09:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, I don't know exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They always do it alone every time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's very mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.62,0:09:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really trust Cheng Xiaoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he'll do\Nanything questionable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there no justice in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you beat up the person\Nwho's going to help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... Hmm,\NI... realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's mainly Lu Guang's effort,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheng Xiaoshi is just a tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lu Guang being reliable is good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheng Xiaoshi,\Nwhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just realized,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after entering the photo,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what I say, goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do whatever I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xu Shanshan,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there are two internship positions\Nat my mom's hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we date,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she said that she could\Narrange a position for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, she doesn't really like\Ngirls with long hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xu Shanshan,\Nyou're going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you want to reject me,\Nyou shouldn't ruin yourself like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a joke,\Nwhy is he having a breakdown?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:10:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That boy looked quite tough,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why is his heart so fragile?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.33,0:11:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheng Xiaoshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,be careful with your current identity,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't get Xu Shanshan in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.42,0:11:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to reiterate\Nthe three rules we agreed on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.45,0:11:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't start chanting\Nyour cursed incantation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.08,0:11:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xu Shanshan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems there's no one sitting here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This feeling... is here again,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and her heart is beating\Nso much faster than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My chest feels so uncomfortable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay attention\Nto where you put your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.42,0:11:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you don't need to be so polite with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that temper of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid that if I don't ask you first,\Nyou'd hit me till I run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xu Shanshan,\Ntake a photo with Dong Yi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so shy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lose! is here again,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again! Again! Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xu Shanshan,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's been so many years, yet none of us\Nhave heard you sing before,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why don't you sing a song today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick any song,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can sing anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.37,0:11:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're usually quite restrained,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:11:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're a little strange today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:12:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This heartbeat is making me\Nso uncomfortable, I can't not drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.62,0:12:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheng Xiaoshi,\Nlater you'll be drinking a bit too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After you come back, remember to go\Ndownstairs and sleep on the couch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder Xu Shanshan got drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.67,0:12:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem like you have\Nanything to worry about,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you need to drink\Nto ease your sorrows, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You nerd, why are you always so rational?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you follow your heart,\Nat least once?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why I chose\Nto further study back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.04,0:12:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because in our four years of university,\NI've already gotten so used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotten used to having meals with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,going to class with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,playing games together,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,taking walks aimlessly around the campus,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.04,0:12:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,speaking thoughtless words\Nthat we both understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,further studying had become\Na means for me to escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have to choose\Nto leave eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I care so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:12:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's why I couldn't bring myself to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so afraid that the answer\Nis not going to be what I think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Xu Shanshan,\Nthe song we picked for you is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, take the mic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to trick me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you use your brain a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you always start without\Nwaiting for everyone to be ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:13:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a good opportunity\Nto take down the enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you guys are just slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you three look a little lively?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like three joss\Nsticks stuck in an urn,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where's the fun in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let me see if
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you ruined my handsome face
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with a blurry photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Go away.\N--Remember to come back often!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't easy to pass\Nthe oral defense, stop cursing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dong Yi,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from now on it's up to you\Nto take care of our beautiful Miss Xu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you think\Nit's such a coincidence that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the both of us decided to further study?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's so many of us who stayed\Nbehind to further study after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.79,0:14:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow morning's class\Nis still at Yi Fu Building 201,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't forget our usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.21,0:14:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,two fried eggs, slightly spicy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one sausage, no coriander.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.25,0:14:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.21,0:14:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never want to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can really sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xu Shanshan,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that\Nafter six years of friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never realized that\Nyou could sing so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was pretty good,\Nyour breathing was quite stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever he speaks,\Nher heart beats like crazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the only way is to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep drinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My fellow brothers and sisters,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's keep singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you guys next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope you all get rich in the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.75,0:15:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's keep in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, my fellow classmates!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.29,0:15:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, Dong Yi,\N--Hey, Xu Shanshan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--be careful.\N--Let's keep in touch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bye!\N--Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go, no one is allowed to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're all already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should join me\Nfor another round!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The signal is pretty weak here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get a ride,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go over to that side and try.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them can leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.29,0:15:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except for you,\Nyou're not allowed to go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:15:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So far so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:16:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more and we're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xu Shanshan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This person is so sneaky,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why does he look so familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the serial killer from the photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.21,0:16:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheng Xiaoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.45,0:16:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let him get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xu Shanshan, are you sober now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, my head is still dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why are you going there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheng Xiaoshi,\Nhave you lost your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just saw the suspect\Nfrom the surveillance photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be foolish,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.42,0:17:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can't catch him on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this guy is more trouble\Nthan human traffickers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can take a photo of his face,\Nat least it could serve as another clue
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to help the police\Nresolve the case earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.25,0:17:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, where's my phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you turn around suddenly,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you might trigger the suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might cause him to attack even quicker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what am I supposed to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to create a situation where\Nhe wouldn't be able to attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then wait for an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't attack, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I drank too much, I need to pee,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:17:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like a waterfall...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...streaming down...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, I forgot I'm a girl now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and find another way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he still intend to attack me\Nwhen I'm like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He truly is a pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, it's for real now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The danger has been eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you learn self defense?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:18:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dong Yi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:18:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the guy with the baseball cap?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this the mama's boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.16,0:19:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a case of unrequited love\Nfrom a male classmate
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who had the wrong intentions,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how did it get so exaggerated\Nand turned into a resolved urban mystery?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this bunch of unscrupulous media\Nhave any bottom line?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.91,0:19:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only did they come up with\Nsome baseless and exaggerated headline,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they even published her photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the task going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.21,0:19:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got distracted with catching a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've written everything down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.21,0:19:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure enough, Lu Guang is always reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.45,0:19:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, I almost forgot\Nyou had this ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what exactly did\NDong Yi say back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already passed\Nhis message to Shanshan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xu Shanshan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.66,0:19:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we were getting ready to graduate,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my parents had urged me to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad has arranged everything for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I've known all along\Nthat after I graduate,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's impossible for me\Nto stay in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dong Yi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.08,0:20:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never dared to confess my feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.42,0:20:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you worrying about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was afraid of hurting you, who had\Nstayed by my side for six years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm just worrying\Nabout the oral defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.62,0:20:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.91,0:20:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm meeting with Qiao Ling tonight\Nto watch a movie and relax,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do you want to come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right,\NI have some things to finish up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you'll have to help me take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.71,0:20:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come and get it from you at your\Ndormitory after I get back tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the entrance of\Nthe dormitory is locked,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to throw it down to you\Nfrom the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of you are basically like\Nan old married couple,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why not clarify your relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I have to graduate,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.33,0:20:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally realized,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.21,0:20:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter how hard the future may be,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.79,0:20:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because leaving you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hurts more than anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.21,0:20:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow morning at ten,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he has an important interview\Nat the Union Building,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he hopes that you can accompany him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.04,0:21:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious he's asking Shanshan\Nto make her feelings clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask her\Nif she went this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hehe,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.71,0:21:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so did you accompany him\Nto his interview this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, what a quick reply,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.62,0:21:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems everything went smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.62,0:21:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dong Yi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.08,0:21:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're here to interview\Nfor this company as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost ten o'clock,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what are you doing standing around?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.08,0:21:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll go up in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll head up first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.83,0:21:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the things I said that day\Nmake her angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.54,0:21:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shanshan, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.04,0:22:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Qiao Ling,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.08,0:22:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,call Xu Shanshan and ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.83,0:22:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xu Shanshan,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.33,0:22:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were you the one who sent\Nthat message in the group?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.29,0:22:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.87,0:22:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...show up as promised.
